node.text: Learn how to make these Ice Cream Cone Cupcakes!🍦🧁

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Rosanna Pansino on July 03, 2021. May be an image of icecream and indoor.

node.text:
Cupcakes that look like ice cream cones? Count me in! This is a super simple recipe that is also cute and creative. Just fill a waffle cone halfway with cake batter and bake, then frost to look like a scoop of ice cream. These cupcakes may not cool you off, but they are the perfect summer treat.

Recipe is from my cookbook #bakingallyearround!
